BOTANY: Scientific study of plant life

Category: Science
Base skill: 25% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

The formal, scientific study of plants: classification, biology, and
cultivation. Distinct from Identify Plants, which is the practical
wilderness skill of telling a useful or dangerous plant from a
harmless one in the field.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, biology, identify plants
